    *   *Why:* Incredible developer speed, consistent design system, easy dark mode.
    *   *Replace with:* SCSS or Emotion/Styled Components.
*   **UI Components & Icons:** Radix UI primitives, Lucide React (Icons), Framer Motion (Animations).
